OL,4,CWatts to release charity song
OL,6,F"The letter was just giving some life
OL,7,Fadvice and things like that and that's
OL,8,Fwhat the chorus of the song is
OL,9,Ffundamentally about," Alfie explained.
OL,11,F"The first lyrics of the chorus are
OL,12,F'you gave me hopeless wings and left a
OL,13,Fletter where you tried to say goodbye'.
OL,15,F"And that was what the whole song was
OL,16,Fkind of born out of.
OL,18,F"Me and one of my best mates jam on
OL,19,Fguitar and sing.
