OL,6,F"Three or four months later we
OL,7,Frealised we had a song and then we
OL,8,Fhanded it over to some experts in the
OL,9,Fmusic world.
OL,11,F"And we've managed to professionally
OL,12,Fproduce a song!" he added.
OL,14,F'Hopeless Wings' is being released on
OL,15,Fmajor music platforms such as Spotify
OL,16,Fand Apple Music on October 31.
OL,18,FMoney raised will go to charity
OL,19,FWinston's Wish which helps grieving
OL,20,Fchildren and young people cope with
OL,21,Fthe loss of someone close to them.
