OL,6,FAlfie described growing up as "really,
OL,7,Freally tough" after his mum died of
OL,8,Fbreast cancer which spread to other
OL,9,Fparts of the body.
OL,11,FHe was brought up by his grandmother
OL,12,Fwho was widowed and Alfie said he felt
OL,13,F"very, very different" growing up
OL,14,Fthrough his school years.
OL,16,FHe described releasing the single as a
OL,17,F"full circle moment", adding: "My mum
OL,18,Fused to be in a band before she got
OL,19,Funwell.
