OL,6,F"She really pushed me down the acting
OL,7,Fand music route when I was even really
OL,8,Fyoung.
OL,10,F"So it was something that she'd have
OL,11,Falways wanted to happen anyway."
OL,13,FAlfie said he had singing lessons when
OL,14,Fhe was aged 13, and said the lyrics
OL,15,Ffor the song just came to him.
OL,17,F"Lyrically it's quite powerful, I
OL,18,Freally backed my singing ability
OL,19,Fhere," he said.
