OL,6,F"When my mum passed away we always
OL,7,Fused to set off Chinese lanterns in
OL,8,Fthe UK and we always used to write a
OL,9,Fmessage on them," Alfie said.
OL,11,F"It always used to be a very symbolic
OL,12,Fthing for me and my family.
OL,14,F"So when I heard about lighting them
OL,15,Fon the river it felt like such a good
OL,16,Fopportunity to share my story.
