OL,6,F"I knew that it was going to be shared
OL,7,Fwith a lot of people and it was going
OL,8,Fto be in an environment that I was
OL,9,Fvery comfortable with and had a lot of
OL,10,Fsymbolism attached," Alfie added.
OL,12,FWhether or not a second single will
OL,13,Ffollow 'Hopeless Wings' is still to be
OL,14,Fdecided but Alfie hasn't ruled it out.
OL,16,FA range of merchandise and a social
OL,17,Fmedia campaign will help promote the
